{
  "stem": "17761.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 96.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And what my father did in this occasion to many other-- in this occasion that I told you and many other occasions-- that he never lost his hope for light at tomorrow.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Even when the Russians-- the German were at Stalingrad, and Western Europe was occupied, and the Scandinavian, Norwegian, [INAUDIBLE] was occupied, and the Balkans were occupied.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You couldn't see a spark of light anywhere.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was full of light in his heart.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And his hope-- and he used to say to me, [NON-ENGLISH] When a Jew wakes up in the morning he has to know that today will be better than yesterday, and tomorrow will be even better.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And with this slogan, we went through all this terrible period and I keep it to my heart until nowadays, and I always am optimistic that tomorrow will be a better day.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not organized, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] but [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] occasionally.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I helped many sick people in different-- and whenever I had occasion, I used to be helpful, but not in an organized way.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But somehow I had an association for negativity, a little thing that's interesting, I think, for such a video.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had-- two little things.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One thing, we didn't have a calendar.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My late father, [INAUDIBLE], was a master in calendar, and we wrote every year, by hand, 10 calendars, which were given out, I don't know to whom.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If I would find one of these calendars, I would pay a fortune.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's one thing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the second problem, we had Pesach.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were no matzot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So, wine, you could buy raisins and make some wine.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But how do you make matzot?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we used to buy little boxes called [INAUDIBLE] boxes-- wheat.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
